markets.title: Will H finish 2nd in Norway?
markets.subtitle: :: Conservative Party
markets.rules_primary: If H finishes in 2nd place in the 2025 Norwegian parliamentary election in Norway according to the certified results, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Ranking is determined by the specified counting method. For proportional representation: rank follows the electoral authority's final seat allocation order. In case of exact ties, markets resolve proportionally (1/number of tied entities). If the election is cancelled or postponed beyond expiration, all markets resolve to No.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if certified election results are published.
